profile: Our goal at Burkley Custom Upholstery is to give the consumer the ability to create their own personalized furniture pieces. We help those who struggle with finding that perfect piece of furniture that fits their lifestyle, a comfortable and unique way to design and create exactly what they are looking for.  We offer a one stop shop in-home, in-store, and online. What makes us different is our modern approach to custom furniture and upholstery.  We make it accessible to the everyday consumer without compromising quality, and as a result, the consumer is able to design furniture that is an authentic expression of who they are or aspire to be.
